Class KanjiListFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.widget.Filter
      • com.dev.yvgenijsharovskij.n5kanjiandkanjistoryquiz.kanjilist.KanjiListFilter

  • public class KanjiListFilter
extends android.widget.Filter
    A android.widget.Filter class to constrain data with a filtering pattern. Used for a Searchable configuration for the KanjiListFragment.KanjiAdapter Filterable-derived class to implement a search functionality for the kanjilist.
